quote: “You cannot ask fate for the life you want while neglecting the man who must deserve it.”
author: Seneca
what_it_means_to_me: This means that the input we give in reflects in our result. Praying for our results to be amazing requires the same and more about of hardwork as the feed. Without hardwork, success doesn't arrive. Thus, to achieve success and expected results, one must put in the same and a lot amount of hardwork, sincerity and consistency. 
